="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5DA1;</span></a><a href="/whv/噘"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5658;</span></a><a href="/whv/劂"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5282;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/B%C3%ACnh-N%C3%B9ng-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-MUqZUPpS1nqY9hEcAzBumA">Bình Nùng chiếu - 平儂詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/author-1nK0o5kpegP7HCXcX0Dr5g">Lý Thái Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/Chinh-ho%C3%A0n-qu%C3%A1-Bi%E1%BB%87n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-ng%E1%BB%99-b%E1%BA%A1o-phong-s%E1%BA%ADu-v%C5%A9-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o-vu-thi%C3%AAn/poem-102RW_3SlibLWJMV72QGXA">Chinh hoàn quá Biện khẩu, ngộ bạo phong sậu vũ, đảo vu thiên - 征還過汴口，遇暴風驟雨，禱于天</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/author-1RfRsGNVNQbtjX629ZNHvQ">Lý Thái Tổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/C%E1%BB%91-t%C3%ADch-th%E1%BA%A7n-t%E1%BB%AB-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-VfQsBh5YWl5of84MPx_PIw">Cố tích thần từ bi ký - 古跡神祠碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-H%C3%A0-Ninh-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n/poem-wW--Ls6Jp03hc-G-Bety4A">Điếu Hà Ninh tổng đốc Hoàng đại nhân - 吊河寧總督黃大人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90%C3%ACnh-th%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-s%C3%A1ch/poem-rF91EB30-zT6DtZAE4A1yw">Đình thí đối sách - 廷試對策</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/Tr%E1%BA%A3m-x%C3%A0-ki%E1%BA%BFm-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mnvnyA6k6RfA2JMT5OVyQ">Trảm xà kiếm phú - 斬蛇劍賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/author-_3sTvaRn7XDoRGq_884L9Q">Sử Hy Nhan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
